# rigx-generated (in any subproject)
**/flake.nix
# …except this repo's own root flake.nix: rigx is installable from its flake
# (`nix profile install github:unofficialtools/rigx/stable`), so the root
# flake.nix must ship in the repo. It's codegen-owned — regenerate with
# `rigx lock` and commit the result.
!/flake.nix
**/output/
result
nixpkgs-pkg/

